quran[16]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,109,"Àlàáfíà kí ó máa bá (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm."
  37,110,"Báyẹn ni A ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)."
  37,111,"Dájúdájú ó wà nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Wa, àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo."
  38,88,"Àti pé dájúdájú ẹ máa mọ ìró rẹ̀ (sí òdodo) láìpẹ́."
  39,73,"Àti pé A óò kó àwọn tó bẹ̀rù Olúwa wọn lọ sínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra níjọníjọ, títí di ìgbà tí wọ́n bá dé ibẹ̀, wọ́n máa ṣí àwọn ìlẹ̀kùn rẹ̀ sílẹ̀ (fún wọn). Àwọn ẹ̀ṣọ́ rẹ̀ yó sì sọ fún wọn pé: “Kí àlàáfíà máa ba yín. Ẹ̀yin dára (nítorí iṣẹ́ yín tó dára). Nítorí náà, ẹ wọ inú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra, (kí ẹ di) olùṣegbére(nínú rẹ̀).”1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Àwọn nasọ̄rọ̄ lérò pé āyah wọ̀nyí, āyah 71 títí dé āyah 73, tako sūrah Mọryam; 19:71. Èsì rẹ̀ ti wà nínú ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ āyah 71 yẹn nínú sūrah Mọryam.]
  39,74,"Wọ́n á sọ pé: “Gbogbo ẹyìn ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu, Ẹni tí Ó mú àdéhùn Rẹ̀ ṣẹ fún wa. Ó tún jogún ilẹ̀ náà fún wa, tí à ń gbé níbikíbi tí a bá fẹ́ nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra.” Ẹ̀san àwọn olùṣe-rere mà sì dára."
  39,75,"O sì máa rí àwọn Mọlāika tí wọ́n ń rọkiriká ní àyíká Ìtẹ́-ọlá. Wọ́n ń ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ àti ìdúpẹ́ fún Olúwa wọn. A máa fi òdodo ṣèdájọ́ láààrin àwọn ẹ̀dá. Wọ́n sì máa sọ pé: “Gbogbo ẹyìn ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu, Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá.”"
  40,52,"Ní ọjọ́ tí àwáwí àwọn alábòsí kò níí ṣe wọ́n ní àǹfààní; ègún ń bẹ fún wọn, ilé (ìyà) burúkú sì wà fún wọn."
  40,53,"Dájúdájú A fún (Ànábì) Mūsā ní ìmọ̀nà. A sì jogún Tírà fún àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl."
  40,54,"(Ó jẹ́) ìmọ̀nà àti ìrántí fún àwọn onílàákàyè."
  41,31,"Àwa ni ọ̀rẹ́ yín nínú ìṣẹ̀mí ayé àti ní ọ̀run. Ohun tí ẹ̀mí yín ń fẹ́ ti wà fún yín nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra. Ohun tí ẹ̀ ń bèèrè fún sì ti wà nínú rẹ̀."
  41,32,"Ó jẹ́ n̄ǹkan ìgbàlejò (fún yín) láti ọ̀dọ̀ Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run.”"
  41,33,"Ta ni ó dára jùlọ ní ọ̀rọ̀ sísọ ju ẹni tí ó pèpè sí ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu, tí ó ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, tí ó sì sọ pé: “Dájúdájú èmi wà nínú àwọn mùsùlùmí.”",footnotes:1:[Kò sí ẹni tí ó dára jù ú lọ]
  42,16,"Àwọn tó ń bá (Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -) jà nípa (ẹ̀sìn) Allāhu lẹ́yìn ìgbà tí àwọn ènìyàn ti gbà fún un, ẹ̀rí wọn máa wó lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa wọn. Ìbínú ń bẹ lórí wọn. Ìyà líle sì wà fún wọn."
  42,17,"Allāhu ni Ẹni tí Ó sọ Tírà (al-Ƙur’ān) àti (òfin) òṣùwọ̀n (déédé) kalẹ̀ pẹ̀lú òdodo.Àti pé kí l’ó máa fi mọ̀ ọ́ pé ó ṣeé ṣe kí Àkókò náà ti súnmọ́! {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo sūrah ar-Rahmọ̄n;  55:7-9.]
  42,18,"Àwọn tí kò ní ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo nínú rẹ̀ ń wá a pẹ̀lú ìkánjú. Àwọn tó sì gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo ń páyà rẹ̀. Wọ́n sì mọ̀ pé dájúdájú òdodo ni. Kíyè sí i, dájúdájú àwọn tó ń jiyàn nípa Àkókò náà ti wà nínú ìṣìnà tó jìnnà."